msgid ""
"Patch version releases will be released to fix documentation issues, "
"usage bugs, and ``minor`` or ``informational`` vulnerabilities found in "
"Vyper. Patch releases should only update error messages and documentation"
" issues relating to its external API."
msgstr "补丁版本将发布以修复文档问题、使用错误以及在 Vyper 中发现的 ``次要`` 或 ``信息性`` 漏洞。补丁版本应仅更新与其外部 API 相关的错误消息和文档问题。"

